        <abstract> 
<p>G. B. Wollaston [in "British Orchideae", <hi rend="italic">Phytologist</hi> n.s. 1 (1855–6): 225–7] says <hi rend="italic">Ophrys arachnites</hi> is a hybrid, which contradicts CD, who says it is a new species.</p> 
